            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-05-30</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>More reliable Self-Managed license recovery.</strong>
NameQuick now handles older Self-Managed licenses more consistently
after restarting, reinstalling, or signing in again on the same
Mac.</li>
<li><strong>Clearer device-limit recovery.</strong> When a license needs
a device slot freed up, NameQuick now keeps the right recovery state
visible instead of getting stuck on a loading screen.</li>
<li><strong>Safer subscription credit display.</strong> Subscription
credits now appear only after NameQuick has confirmed the active
subscription details, keeping syncing states clear while billing data
loads.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed Self-Managed licenses getting stuck on
launch.</strong> Older licenses should no longer hang during startup
while NameQuick checks activation status.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed same-device activation recovery.</strong> NameQuick
now more reliably recognizes valid activation evidence from the same Mac
instead of incorrectly reporting that no device slots are
available.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed license repair after account changes.</strong>
Returning from license management now retries the right recovery path
and keeps the app state accurate if the device slot still needs
attention.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
